OL,3,CAdam Peaty: 'Faith got me out of
OL,4,Cdepression struggle and back in the
OL,5,Cpool'
OL,7,FThree-time Olympic champion Adam Peaty
OL,8,Fis looking to win his third 100m
OL,9,Fbreaststroke gold in a row and credits
OL,10,Ffinding faith with helping him return
OL,11,Fto the pool, as Ben Chapman reports
OL,13,FBritain's most successful ever male
OL,14,FOlympic swimmer has told ITV News he
OL,15,Fdid not think he would be in the pool
OL,16,Ffor the 2024 Paris Games but now he
OL,17,Fwants to equal US star Michael Phelps.
