OL,3,CAdam Peaty: 'Faith got me out of
OL,4,Cdepression struggle and back in the
OL,5,Cpool'
OL,7,FAdam Peaty says he's aiming to defend
OL,8,Fhis Olympic 100 metre breaststroke
OL,9,Ftitle for a second time, a feat only
OL,10,Fachieved once before by Phelps.
OL,12,FBut for a number of years, Peaty's
OL,13,Fswimming career was thrown into doubt
OL,14,Fafter a struggle with his mental
OL,15,Fhealth kept him out of the pool.
OL,17,FHe said his faith and determination
OL,18,Fhelped him pull through.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/5
