OL,3,CAdam Peaty: 'Faith got me out of
OL,4,Cdepression struggle and back in the
OL,5,Cpool'
OL,7,F"You know, it's been a very hard road,
OL,8,Fa very hard just up and down and
OL,9,Ftrying to find a way through it,
OL,10,Ftrying to find a way to be positive
OL,11,Fevery single day or even get to
OL,12,Ftraining," the Team GB swimmer said.
OL,14,F"A few communities have helped me,
OL,15,Fmassively one in my church. I go every
OL,16,FSunday in Nottingham.
OL,18,F"In sport, it's a very lonely journey
OL,19,Fwhere you're having those internal
OL,20,Fquestions every single day."
