OL,3,CAdam Peaty: 'Faith got me out of
OL,4,Cdepression struggle and back in the
OL,5,Cpool'
OL,7,FDespite his success, Peaty has found
OL,8,Fthe three years since the last
OL,9,FOlympics in Tokyo difficult. He broke
OL,10,Fup with the mother of his young son
OL,11,Fand struggled with depression and
OL,12,Falcoholism.
OL,14,FBut now the 29-year-old is ready to
OL,15,Fgive the Olympic Games in Paris his
OL,16,F"best approach".
OL,18,FHe said: "Honestly, it isn't about the
OL,19,Fgold medals, and everyone's probably
OL,20,Fthinking BS right. But for me it it
OL,21,Freally isn't.
