OL,3,CAdam Peaty: 'Faith got me out of
OL,4,Cdepression struggle and back in the
OL,5,Cpool'
OL,7,F"I can't go into that Olympic Games in
OL,8,FParis with all that pressure of I've
OL,9,Fgot to win I've got to win.
OL,11,F"It's my third one in a row,
OL,12,Fpotentially, I've got to go in now
OL,13,Fpeace peacefully and calmly and go."
